{"tid":34304,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"老婆Yoyo咀女 王浩信「復仇」搞HeHe","createTime":"2016-12-11T11:48:18.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T12:23:32.000Z","uid":62377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1cf55e82126b6f137bf35f9961e77661154e1d0e","tid":34304,"uid":62377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T11:48:18.000Z","msg":"【東方日報專訊】藝人王浩信與陳自瑤（Yoyo）昨日夫妻檔出席MCP新都城中心聖誕活動，浩信透露因台慶劇《致命復活》效應而多了不少賺外快機會，還帶挈太太，故非常感恩。對於丈夫在兩線台慶劇均受觀眾喜愛，Yoyo表示高興，但浩信卻重提她與陳煒於《幕後玩家》的咀戲：「淨係睇相都火滾！好在我新劇《踩過界》都同張振朗玩HeHe，唔係咀，係沖涼！」Yoyo笑說：「我以為佢幫你擦背添！但估唔到中港粉絲接受到我同女性Kiss，仲話鍾意。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，浩信表示日前外景時遇上影帝周潤發：「最開心係佢問我圍頭話係咪好難學，證明佢有睇套劇（《EU超時任務》）。（有冇叫發哥投你視帝一票？）相信佢眼睛係雪亮嘅。」而對於李潤庭爆婚外情，浩信與Yoyo表示維繫夫妻關係最重要是溝通及信任。"},{"pid":"57473021885f8e3d7c55d3ae05f6a0c1bf6ee078","tid":34304,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T11:50:39.000Z","msg":"仲記得馬明個啲同佢講 我真係恭喜你"},{"pid":"1edcee4bb2a74076f3f3663cca8a68eac486726b","tid":34304,"uid":4037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T11:56:52.000Z","msg":"喂呀"},{"pid":"fac769690929241b3494c74b82ef442b808e2165","tid":34304,"uid":17198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:02:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/11/200242_e98408e10bc9e4468eccfc0052e828f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F11%2F200242_e98408e10bc9e4468eccfc0052e828f2.jpg&h=cf13c1b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9616a8b180f518cffa5ef74d025fce53dc68fc28","tid":34304,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:03:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/11/200242_e98408e10bc9e4468eccfc0052e828f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F11%2F200242_e98408e10bc9e4468eccfc0052e828f2.jpg&h=cf13c1b2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"